  {name: "Canel's 4-Pack Chiclets Gum: 300-Piece Tub", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\">Yummy bubblegum tab 4-packs in an assortment of the following 5 flavors: <b>Blueberry, Cinnamon, Fruit, Peppermint, and Spearmint.</b><br><br>Unit Price = $0.05/pack.<br><br>Tub contains 300 Canel's Chewing Gum Tabs 4-Packs.<br><br>Shipping Weight ~ 4 lbs.</p>", price: "15.0", sale_price: nil, code: "2393", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-127692.jpg"},
  {name: "Caramel - Cashew - Cranberry Trail Mix: 25LB Case", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\">Milk chocolate chips, caramel balls, plump cashews, cranberries, golden raisins, almonds, and more have been combined together to create this amazing trail mix! <br><br>Unit Price = 7.90/lb.<br><br>Case contains 25 pounds of Caramel, Cashew, and Cranberry Trail Mix.<br><br>Shipping Weight ~ 26 lbs.</p>", price: "147.5", sale_price: nil, code: "2828", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-130498.jpg"},
  {name: "Carousel Gumball Machine - Petite", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\"></p> <div>Shiny red mini gumball machine! Classic gumball machine constructed of sturdy cast metal and a glass globe. This machine accepts pennies, nickels, dimes, and quarters; or, it can be adjusted for free dispensing. There is no way to adjust the machine to accept only one type of coin, but you can adjust the amount of product it dispenses.<br><br><b>Total Height:</b> 9 Inches<br><br> It dispenses 1/2-inch gumballs and has a 13-ounce capacity.<br><br> Gumballs sold separately.<br><br> Shipping Weight ~ 3 lbs.</div>", price: "19.9", sale_price: nil, code: "2787", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-127444.jpg"},
  {name: "Carousel Gumball Machine -Junior", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\">Classic gumball machine constructed of sturdy cast metal and a glass globe. This machine accepts pennies, nickels, dimes, and quarters; or, it can be adjusted for free dispensing. There is no way to adjust the machine to accept only one type of coin, but you can adjust the amount of product it dispenses.<br><br><b>Total Height:</b> 12 Inches<br><br>Machine dispenses 1/2 inch gumballs and has a 24-ounce capacity.<br><br>Gumballs sold separately.<br><br>Shipping Weight ~ 5 lbs.</p>", price: "35.0", sale_price: nil, code: "2788", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-127443.jpg"},
  {name: "Carousel Gumball Machine -King", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\">Give the knob a twirl and out pops a sweet treat! This classic gumball machine has a durable metal base, and a glass globe that holds 62 ounces of 1/2-inch gumballs. It can also be used to dispense peanuts or candy! This machine accepts pennies, nickels, dimes, and quarters; or, it can be adjusted for free dispensing.<br><br><b>Total Height:</b> 15 Inches <br><br>There is no way to adjust the machine to accept only one type of coin, but you can adjust the amount of product it dispenses.<br>Candy and gumballs sold separately!<br><br>Shipping Weight ~ 8 lbs.</p>", price: "49.5", sale_price: nil, code: "2789", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-127442.jpg"},
