  {name: "Just Born Assorted Jelly Beans: 4.5LB Bag", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\"></p> <div>Traditional jelly beans in assorted flavors and colors. Just Born jelly beans are packed with mouth-watering flavor for an absolutely yummy experience! Assortment may include:<br><b>Cherry - Red<br> Grape - Purple<br> Lemon - Yellow<br> Licorice - Black<br> Lime - Green<br> Orange - Orange<br> Pineapple - White<br> Strawberry - Pink</b><br><br> There are approximately 260 pieces per pound.<br><br> Unit Price = $3.00/lb.<br><br> Bag contains 4.5 pounds of Just Born Assorted Jelly Beans Candy.<br> Made in the USA.<br><br> Shipping Weight ~ 5 lbs. Kosher Certified.<br><br><b>DISCLAIMER:</b> Color assortment may vary from bag to bag. NO REFUNDS for MISSING COLORS or COLOR variance.</div>", price: "13.5", sale_price: nil, code: "2444", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-125970.jpg"},
  {name: "Kabaya Assorted Melon Hard Candy: 300-Piece Box", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\">A unique assortment of melon flavored hard candies. The yellow and red melon pieces have a swirl of green like the rind of a watermelon. They even feature little black specks to mimic watermelon seeds. The pink ball piece is all watermelon flavor with a soft, fizzy effervesence. Each piece is wrapped to seal in freshness.<br><br>Unit Price = $0.15/piece.<br><br>Box contains 330 pieces of Kabaya Assorted Melon Hard Candy packed in 12 bags. Imported from Japan.<br><br>Shipping Weight ~ 4 lbs.</p>", price: "45.0", sale_price: nil, code: "2734", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-128661.jpg"},
  {name: "Kasugai Fizzing Cola Hard Candy: 3.78-Ounce Bag", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\"></p> <div>Fun hard candy discs featuring a yummy cola flavor and a fizzing, carbonated sensation. Each piece is wrapped to seal in freshness.<br><br> Unit Price = $0.35/piece.<br><br> Bag contains 3.78 ounces of Kasugai Fizzing Cola Hard Candy...that's about 15 pieces. Made in Japan.<br><br> Shipping Weight ~ 1/2 lb.</div>", price: "5.25", sale_price: nil, code: "2732", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-129745.jpg"},
  {name: "Kasugai Fizzing Soda Hard Candy: 4.41-Ounce Bag", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\">Fun hard candy discs featuring an assortment of yummy soda flavors and a fizzing, carbonated sensation. Each piece is wrapped to seal in freshness.<br><br>Unit Price = $0.25/piece.<br><br>Bag contains 3.78 ounces of Kasugai Fizzing Soda Hard Candy....<br><br>that's about 15 pieces. Made in Japan.<br><br>Shipping Weight ~ 1/2 lb.</p>", price: "5.0", sale_price: nil, code: "2733", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-129746.jpg"},
  {name: "Kasugai Flower Kiss Hard Candy: 20-Piece Bag", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\"></p> <div>Unique flower scented hard candies in an assortment of refreshing designs like violet, rose, daffodil, and more. Each piece is wrapped to seal in freshness.<br><br> Unit Price = $0.25/piece.<br><br> Bag contains 20 pieces of Kasugai Flower Hard Candy.<br><br> Imported from Japan.<br><br> Shipping Weight ~ 1/2 lb.</div>", price: "5.0", sale_price: nil, code: "2729", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-128148.jpg"},
  {name: "Kasugai Lychee Hard Candy: 24-Piece Bag", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\">Lichi, also spelled lychee, is an exotic tropical fruit with a sweet taste and a fragrant smell. Now this unique flavor has been infused into gourmet white hard candies to create a truly unique confectionery experience. Each piece is wrapped to seal in freshness.<br><br>Unit Price = $0.20/piece.<br><br>Bag contains 24 pieces of wrapped Kasugai Lychee Fruit Hard Candy.<br><br>Imported from Japan.<br><br>Shipping Weight ~ 1/2 lb.</p>", price: "4.8", sale_price: nil, code: "2730", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-127600.jpg"},
  {name: "Kasugai Ramune Candy Assortment: 4.2-Ounce Bag", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\">Delicious sweet tart candies in an assortment of fruity flavors!<br><br>Bag contains 4.2 ounces of wrapped Kasugai Ramune Assorted Candy.<br>Imported from Japan.<br><br>Shipping Weight ~ 1/2 lb.</p>", price: "5.0", sale_price: nil, code: "2738", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-130802.jpg"},
  {name: "Key Lime Salt Water Taffy: 3LB Bag", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\"></p> <div>Delicious green salt water taffy candy with a perky key lime flavor!<br><br> There are about 65 pieces per pound.<br><br> Unit Price = $3.30/lb.<br><br> Bag contains 3 pounds of Green Swirled Key Lime Salt Water Taffy.<br> Made in the USA.<br><br> Shipping Weight ~ 4 lbs. Kosher Certified.</div>", price: "9.9", sale_price: nil, code: "2550", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/130667_ic.jpg"},
  {name: "King Size Hershey Milk Chocolate Candy Bars: 18-Piece Box", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\">The king size version of the classic Hershey Milk Chocolate Bar!<br><br>Unit Price = $2.00/bar.<br><br>Display box contains 18 King-Size Hershey's Milk Chocolate Candy Bars, each with a net weight of 2.6 ounces.<br><br>Shipping Weight ~ 4 lbs. Kosher Certified.</p>", price: "36.0", sale_price: nil, code: "2608", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-128301.jpg"},
  {name: "King Size Hershey Milk Chocolate with Almonds Bars: 18-Piece Box", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\">The king size version of the classic Hershey Milk Chocolate with Almonds Bar. The perfect snack any time of day!<br><br>Unit Price = $2.00/bar.<br><br>Display box contains 18 King-Size Hershey's Milk Chocolate with Almonds Candy Bars, each with a net weight of 2.6 ounces.<br><br>Shipping Weight ~ 4 lbs.</p>", price: "36.0", sale_price: nil, code: "2609", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-129764.jpg"},
  {name: "Kit Kat Candy Bars: 36-Piece Box", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\">Break me off a piece of that.... you know the rest.<br><br>Unit Price = $1.00/bar.<br><br>Display box contains 36 crispy Kit Kat Candy Bars, each with a net weight of 1.5 ounces.<br><br>Shipping Weight ~ 5 lbs. Kosher Certified.</p>", price: "36.0", sale_price: nil, code: "2337", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-127372.jpg"},
  {name: "Konpeito Prickly Hard Candy Balls: 5.42-Ounce Bag", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\">Fun hard candy balls with nodules protruding in all directions.... they look like giant candy spores! This collection of unique rock candy features an assortment of bright colors and a delicious sweet flavor. Perfect for treat bowls and candy buffets!<br><br><b>Candy Diameter:</b> 1/2 Inch<br><br>Bag contains 5.42 ounces of Konpeito Hard Candy Prickly Balls.<br><br>Made in Japan.<br><br>Shipping Weight ~ 1/2 lb.</p>", price: "5.0", sale_price: nil, code: "2722", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-129744.jpg"},
  {name: "Laser Projector Pops: 12-Piece Box", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\"></p> <div>Project fun shapes like hearts, eyeballs, smiley faces, kitty faces, stars, and soccer balls with these light projecting candy rods. Works up to 10 feet indoors in normal lighting and even further in the dark!<br><br> Assortment includes 3 fabulous lollipop flavors:<br><b>Blue Raspberry Rage, Cherry Blast, and Strawberry Burst.</b><br><br><b>Sucker Dimensions-</b><br> Length: 5 1/8 Inches<br> Diameter: 1 Inch</div> <div> <br> Unit Price = $1.65/pop.<br><br> Display box contains 12 Laser Projector Lollipops.<br><br> Shipping Weight ~ 3 lbs. Kosher Certified.</div>", price: "19.8", sale_price: nil, code: "2669", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-127011.jpg"},
  {name: "Lavender Big Fat Giant Marshmallows: 25-Piece Bag", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\"></p> <div>A CandyWarehouse.com EXCLUSIVE!<br><br> Having company? If you’re worried some ghost will raid your refrigerator, pelt the Stay Puft Marshmallow man with these purple Big Fat Marshmallows. Then, empty your proton pack into a bowl and put your party in the purple.<br><br><b>Marshmallow Dimensions (Inches):</b> 2 x 2 x 2<br><br> Unit Price = $0.25/piece.<br><br> Bag contains 25 Lavender Purple Giant Marshmallows.<br><br> Shipping Weight ~ 2 lbs.</div> <div> </div> <div> <b>DISCLAIMER:</b> Color may vary from photographs. Manufacturing process often differs slightly with every batch. NO REFUNDS for COLOR variance.</div>", price: "6.25", sale_price: nil, code: "2579", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-130092.jpg"},
