  {name: "Life Savers Candy Singles - 13 Flavors Assortment: 1100-Piece Case", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\"></p> <div>Your favorite little Life Savers candies.... with a cellophane wrapper around every piece! Perfect for the open candy jar in your life.<br><br> Assortment includes 13 fabulous flavors:<br><b>Watermelon, Green Apple, Pineapple, Mango Melon, Cherry, Fruit Punch, Pina Colada, Tangerine, Banana, Grape, Orange, Lemon, and Raspberry.</b><br><br> Unit Price = $0.05/piece.<br><br> Case contains 1,100 LifeSavers Singles Candy Assortment packed in 12 bags, each with a net weight of 13 ounces.<br><br> Shipping Weight ~ 11 lbs.</div>", price: "55.0", sale_price: nil, code: "2306", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/Lifesavers-ff-130623.jpg"},
