  {name: "Light Blue Rock Candy Crystal Sticks: 120-Piece Case", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\"></p> <div>Flavored with cotton candy, these light blue candy crystalline sugar structures on a stick are perfect for decorating!<br><br> There are approximately 4 inches of rock candy on each stick.<br><br><b>Total Length:</b> 6 Inches<br><br> Unit Price = $0.75/stick.<br><br> Case contains 120 unwrapped Light Blue Rock Candy Crystal Sticks.<br> Made in the USA.<br><br> Shipping Weight ~ 10 lbs. Kosher Certified.</div>", price: "90.0", sale_price: nil, code: "2519", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/crystal-sticks-light-blue-w.jpg"},
