  {name: "Princess Candy Necklaces & Bracelets: 24-Piece Box", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\"></p> <div>Pretty pink and white candy beads featuring a delicious strawberry flavor are formed into fun stretchable necklaces and bracelets! A pink candy tiara dangles from each piece of this royal jewelry.<br><br><b>Necklace Specifications-</b><br> Diameter: 5 Inches<br> Tiara Charm Width: 1 Inch<br><br><b>Bracelet Specifications-</b><br> Diameter: 2 1/2 Inches<br> Tiara Charm Width: 1 Inch<br><br> Unit Price = $0.35/piece.<br><br> Box contains 24 pieces of wrapped Pink and White Princess Candy Jewelry, 12 each of Necklaces and Bracelets.<br><br> Shipping Weight ~ 1 lb.</div>", price: "8.4", sale_price: nil, code: "2777", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-127980.jpg"},
  {name: "Psychedelic Swirl 5-Inch Lollipops: 12-Piece Box", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\"></p> <div>Dude, these suckers are way radical.... swirling with crazy colors!<br> Each pop has a yummy cherry flavor.<br><br><b>Sucker Specifications-</b><br> Net Weight: 5 Ounces<br> Diameter: 5 Inches<br> Total Length: 11 Inches<br><br> Unit Price = $2.45/pop.<br><br> Box contains 12 cellophane wrapped Psychedelic Rainbow Lollipops.<br> Made in the USA.<br><br> Shipping Weight ~ 6 lbs.<br><br><b>ATTENTION:</b> These suckers are handmade by people.<br> Swirl shape and candy color shade may vary by manufacturing batch.</div>", price: "29.4", sale_price: nil, code: "2458", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-127353.jpg"},
