  {name: "Wiggle & Giggle Pops: 12-Piece Box", description: "<br><p id=\"longDescription\"></p> <div>Silly, giggling smiley face balls wiggle on top of a spring as you wave these fun lollipops from side to side. Assortment includes 3 fabulous flavors: <b>Bubble Gum, Cotton Candy, and Root Beer.</b><br><br> Unit Price = $1.65/pop.<br><br> Display box contains 12 Wiggle &amp; Giggle Lollipops.<br><br> Shipping Weight ~ 3 lbs. Kosher Certified.</div>", price: "19.8", sale_price: nil, code: "2759", image: "http://www.candywarehouse.com//assets/item/regular/image-127152.jpg"},
